Changelog: - removed turning on of sv_cheats - added slow-motion on break - added low-gravity on break (generator) - added refract-overlay on break - added speed-tunnel connections between the rooms - added new lightnings in dystopia-room - removed 3d skybox for better performance I recommend at least 32 players to have on the map! It runs very good on the Zombie ZEUS Server, which everyone should know ;) You need to have Es_tools and Eventscripts installed to run the map well with extra effects! Update: Added custom-textures into bsp file with bsp-zip cause Man didn't worked properly! Pls redownload map.
